  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the fondue pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the lamb pieces and cook until browned on all sides.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the kombu cold extract, dried apricots, prunes, cumin, paprika, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 2 hours.",
    "Remove the lid and cook for an additional 30 minutes.",
    "Serve the lamb and sauce hot, garnished with fresh parsley.",
    "Traditionally, this dish is served with crusty bread or over couscous."
